description: TEHRAN – Iran freestyle team won the title of the 2024 Asian Wrestling Championships on Friday for the sixth time in seven years.

description:
Israel has declared some 1,000 hectares (2,470 acres) of land in the 
occupied West Bank as state territory since launching war on Gaza on October 7, with its seizures in 2024 outpacing any year in history, according to the Haaretz newspaper.

description:
Aran Gallery is playing host to an exhibition of sculptures by Parisa Taqipur. 
The exhibition will run until April 26 at the gallery located at 5 Lolagar St., Neauphle-le-Chateau St.
